{"tid":1345571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無資格反對暴力? 退幾多步諗都唔撚岩 !","createTime":"2019-07-22T02:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:57:36.000Z","uid":202716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"005bbafcdd4e3a36870140dc9908a40ab578398f","tid":1345571,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"首先, <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上環黑警冇預警開槍，而唔係好多人廣傳</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1342566/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1342566/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑社會搞大元朗單野就係想遮住上環開30幾槍</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1341436/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1341436/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n見到有人話:<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">香港人反省下自己當日有無縱容過暴力，認同過暴力，如果有既，你無資格講乜嘢痛心唔痛心，亦都無需要激動，因為你無資格，不要突顯自己的幼稚和偽善。\n重申，反對所有暴力行為。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個講法點諗都唔撚岩!!!</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 退一萬步黎講，示威者有暴力，黑社會有暴力<br />\n兩邊都有，咁點解黑警琴晚唔做野? 警署又落閘? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 退一百步黎講，香港最多得二百萬人遊行，支持成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n咁即係，有五百萬人撐黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但琴晚係無差別攻擊啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警係咪應該要保護起碼 5 / 7 既元朗居民?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 如果睇到呢到你仲覺得冇問題，你可以走喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本，黑警既武力合法性黎自人民，人民比錢你出糧，人民先係你既老細<br />\n人民反對你濫權有咩問題?<br />\n但再反對你 你都要保護市民，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個係你既職責</span></span>!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f81200f1b48c4af65b96cf4441d51333e1e6857","tid":1345571,"uid":13754,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20